Class Product

Object
Product
public class Product extends Object
FUTURE ENHANCEMENT: This class needs equality tests (that is, the implementation of equals and hashCode) so that it can be used in Collection implementations that depend on equality tests for adding and removing elements.

This class represents a product that's managed by an inventory system.

Husnain Arif
